oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Leonard Melton Jr. with five pound bass caught on Kentucky Lake, Tenn.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of Leonard Melton, Jr. with a five-pound bass caught on Kentucky Lake. Melton is stting in fishing boat with tackle box and fishing rod next to him. He is wearing a button down shirt, pants and loafers. In the background there is the lake, tree brush and treeline.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
